wiki.summary: “Come back to me“ is a promotional track on RM’s album, Right Place, Wrong Person, and officially released on streaming platforms on May 10, 2024, alongside an official music video. The song was first performed on the final concert of Agust D’s D-DAY Tour on August 6, 2023, at Jamsil Indoor Stadium in Seoul, South Korea. RM has shared that this is one of his “most treasured songs.” Read more on Last.fm.
